Stinsonshendrinsf Just talked with Stinson and he is going to give Rayfael a call to set up an informal talk He says what they do is bring in people with Rayfaels level of technical expertise but no financial skills as a Sr Specialist so they can learn the business They really dont use the AssociateAnalyst route for hiring people Tell Rayfael to expect the call or he may in fact want to give Stinson a call directly

Enron Jobshendrinsf Forwarded by Julie A GomezHOUECT on PM From Julie A Gomez PM To cc Subject Enron Job Dear Rayfael I did get in contact with the head of our research group today and passed along your resume For your information his name is Stinson Gibner a really nice guy and his phone number here at work is He is the Vice President over the group and sounded interested in talking with you He said that he would call you and set up an informal talk The next step would be to come in for the formal interviews which Scott can tell you how much fun that process is I would suggest that you follow up with Stinson in a couple of days if he has not called you by then The entry level job in Stinsons group for someone with your level of education is called a Sr Speicalist The pay range for this job classification is to At this level you could come in and learn the financial side of the business which will help you to progress through the job hierarchy I am glad to have gotten something productive done today After being gone for a week it was a big fat mess in my office today To top it all off I had to wait at home for over two hours for the police because my house was burglerized while I was in New York last week They just took a couple of rings from my jewerly box nothing big but they were from my trip to Cartegena Columbia and cannot be easily replaced Its always something Oh well Hope you have a great evening Julie

FW FW BIG CATand I thought Ellie was fat Original Message From Cantrell Rebecca Sent Friday May AM To Julie A NRON Subject FW FW BIG CAT You wont believe the size of this cat Forwarded by Rebecca W CantrellHOUECT on AM William Harper on AM To Black Cathy Bracewell Pat Carrera Barb Cantrell Becky Ford Ron Harper Jane Harper Bill Harper Spencer Patterson Paige Schlesinger Henry Schneider Paula Schneider Russell cc Subject FW FW BIG CAT Even if you dont have time to read the story below definitely check out the photo at the end That is one DAMN BIG feline Now this is a Big Cat Mr Degagne recalls how years ago he befriended two stray young cats on the old AECL research facility at Chalk River The kittens had appeared in late summer and apparently had gotten under a security fence around the old labs abandoned since the late s With the help of his tuna sandwich Mr Degagne was able to coax the kitties close enough so that he could pick them up A self described animal lover he did not want to place the kittens in the local Humane Society Later that evening his wife Louise and their two children came to a family decision to keep the kittens which they named Lost and Found Lost was a female and Found was a male When nature finally took its course a litter of kittens was born years later One of the litter was a big white female with unique black markings on her side and tail Something about the kitten captured the hearts of the family and while her siblings eventually found homes elsewhere Snowball stayed with the Degagnes In her years Snowballs size has seemed to snowball Put simply Snowball is no ordinary cat she measures inches from nose to tail and weighs in at lbs She started out a big kitty and she just seemed to keep growing She always meowed for more food and would climb up on the counter to eat food which I forgot to cover Chicken is her favorite Once I left a cooked chicken on the table that I was going to use for a boat picnic an hour later the chicken was gone Louise said We knew that snowball wasnt your average cat when the neighbors German Shepherd ran yelping away from his first encounter with her She just isnt afraid of any animals After we found a half eaten raccoon out by the garage we decided that maybe Snowball should be kept fenced in We soon discovered that while we can keep Snowball in the yard we couldnt keep raccoons from Snowball At least it kept the food bills down Rodger laughed Like all female cats she is very territorial but with us she is just a big ole kitten he said So what does a pound cat eat Snowball goes through about lbs of cat food a day along with cooked chicken supplemented with deer and moose that Rodger hunts in the fall She likes Pike a lot so I don t throw them back any more Snowball often accompanies Rodger fishing on the Ottawa eagerly peering over the side of the boat as soon as his line goes tight So what do the Degagnes attribute Snowballs size to Rodger says Wellthe vet thinks it could be her thyroid but she isnt fat shes just a real big cat I think maybe her parents got into something at Chalk River that they shouldnt have NOW go have a look at Snowball BigCatjpg Re Iroquois Gas Transmissions Eastchester Expansionthe heck is Mirant Corp Julie John NRON AM To Ruth CT Frank W nron Gil NRON Phil NRON David NRON Robin CT Dick CT Brad CT Sean NRON Julie A CT cc Subject Iroquois Gas Transmissions Eastchester Expansion Iroquois has shuffled their customer base for the expansion into New York City beginning in November The following customers have executed binding Precedent Agreements for year contracts that would require a buyout if the shipper tried to exit Volume Con Ed Dthd Keyspan Ravenswood Mirant Corporation Orion Power Virginia Power Energy Marketing Total Dthd Iroquois has changed their interconnect with Con Ed to the Throgs Neck section of the Bronx along the East River They are also starting to plan an expansion of the Eastchester project that will increase deliveries by to Dthd beginning in the time frame This expansion is timed similar to the recently announced plans by DukeKeyspan and El Paso for projects into Long Island Iroquois is targeting NYPA NRG and other announced merchant plants

Capacity Trading System Cc Cathy and Ed Just wanted to let you know my progress on cost estimates and documents The paperwork will be broken down into two documents for the initial phase The first is a Commitment letter an LOI of sorts for just the free posting system we have been talking about It will be followed by a full blown Electronic Transacations Agreement that I am sure will take much longer for all our lawyers to get through I need to get the LOIs done to show our management here the level of commitment we have from our initial launch pipelines and it should be to you within the week I am hoping this short document will not have a tough time getting through your legal processes The next document ETA will closely follow the LOIs but I know will be more of a negotiation since that is where the real details are spelled out We are still in the process of finalizing the costs Gap Analysis and the deliverables for the GIR settlement system requirements I should have more information on this by the end of the week We unfortunately have had some slippage on the start date of phase one due to some scope changes and personnel issues We are definately looking into first quarter of next year so that buys us some time with getting the documents through our respective legal departments I apologize for this delay but once we have the signed LOIs back in our shop we will be able to lock down a launch date Please give me a call if you have any questions I will update you as news breaks Thanks Julie

Exhibits to Kern Predecent Agreementare the completed Exhibit As that are required for the Kern Open Season The bid requires that a seperate Precedent Agreement PA be submitted with each Exhibit A so that means your customers must sign two PAs and submit one Exhibit with each Also the credit worthiness and the affiliate statement must be submitted with each PA Instead of submitting all your affiliates you can instead submit the following statement Shipper warrants and represents that no other affiliate is participating in the open season Julie
